title: Starstruck
overview: Starstruck sees ordinary members of the public with an exceptional talent team up to transform into some of the world's biggest music icons from Amy Winehouse to Ariana Grande, Lionel Richie to Lady Gaga, Marvin Gaye to Michael Buble, and many more in between.  Four teams of three battle it out each week to win the vote of an expert judging panel and virtual audience for a coveted place in the final and to be in with the chance of winning a whopping £50,000.
